data.description: Welcome to 119 Killis Blvd, a charming home in Richlands, NC. This delightful residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this well-maintained property provides ample space for your family. The living area connects the living room, dining area, and modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, stylish cabinetry, and ample counter space for your culinary endeavors. The master suite provides a spacious retreat with an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Step outside to your private backyard oasis, perfect for entertaining or enjoying the Carolina sunshine.What sets this home apart is the thoughtful addition of a 4-stage reverse osmosis drinking water system. Additionally, a whole-home water softening system adds a touch of luxury to daily living, enhancing the longevity of your appliances. This property is not just a house but a place to create lasting memories. Schedule a showing today to experience the unique features and warmth of 119 Killis Blvd. Make this residence your new home.
